729863f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Wild Avenue
729863f-a.text:
Victory Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of Wild Avenue
(north of Lawton Avenue). The house was on the property of
the Lena Decker Estate in 1898 and was owned by Sherman Decker
in 1907.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
